config MV_ETH_PP2_1
	bool "Support PPv2.1 version (A0)"
	default n
 	---help---
	PPv2.1 support (Avanta-LP A0)
	PPv2.1 enable various features such as:
	* Qsets support
	* TX descriptors chunks mechanism
	* See PPv2.1 MAS for more info

